    <name>Use a graphic organizer to help adult learners set and evaluate their math goals</name>
    <intro></intro>
    <introformat>1</introformat>
    <content>&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{4ede78af-78b2-450e-8793-251bff963f31}{67}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:10,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;a data-sessionid="3b70882e-530d-1e40-f94c-53fc4e3e3b94" data-shapeids="8" data-slide=""&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/a&gt;The following instructions have been adapted from the &lt;a href="http://www.utelearning.org/images/resources/2004%20Setting%20GoalsToolkit.CDE.pdf" target="_blank"&gt;Adult Learner Goals Toolkit&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;(download the PDF to access the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;assessment form).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="text-align: right; font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;Give each learner a worksheet. Allow time in class for&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;learners to complete their worksheets.&lt;a data-sessionid="3b70882e-530d-1e40-f94c-53fc4e3e3b94" data-shapeids="8" data-slide=""&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;Gather the completed worksheets. Copy the worksheets for&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;each learner's file.&amp;nbsp;Return the original worksheet to the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;learner, with instructions to keep the worksheet for&amp;nbsp;later&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;review.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;Use the learner responses to inform your instruction and&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;curriculum.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;Completed worksheets can serve as the basis for learner&amp;nbsp;choice of primary and secondary goals&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;for AEFLA reporting&amp;nbsp;purposes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;At regular intervals ask learners to bring out their&amp;nbsp;worksheets (using the copies you have on file&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;for learners who have misplaced theirs) to revisit&amp;nbsp;their goals and check in with the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;following&amp;nbsp;questions:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;Have learners reached their goals in full, in part, or not at all?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;What has&amp;nbsp;helped them?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;What has&amp;nbsp;hindered them?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;Do they have new goals to check?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/Math%20Goals%20Self%20Assessment%20%281%29.png?time=1672697583230" alt="Math Goals Self Assessment Table" width="1700" height="2200" class="img-responsive atto_image_button_middle"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{26243aa0-ffd5-42bc-9f13-143ce67b6471}{152}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:10,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;Go back to the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="$@COURSEVIEWBYID*292@$#section-5" target="_blank"&gt;Try It Yourself Section&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;for a list of all Try it Yourself Options.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol role="list" start="1"&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;​&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/divider%20wave.png" alt="Divider Wave" width="1920" height="195" role="presentation" class="img-responsive atto_image_button_text-bottom"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
